# Ensure Cargo.lock has consistent LF line endings on all platforms.
# Without this, a Windows checkout converts Cargo.lock to CRLF and the
# `hashFiles('**/Cargo.lock')` expression in CI produces a different hash
# than Linux/macOS, which can lead to cache keys that are needlessly
# fragmented or that never match a previously-saved entry.
Cargo.lock text eol=lf
